"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Ben Healy (Ireland) at 1:20  After a relatively sedate first 200km to the longest road race in Olympic history, at 273km, it sparked to life when the Irishman Ben Healy attacked alongside Kazakhstan's Alexey Lutsenko.\", \"from\": 3288, \"to\": 3505, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3288, \"end\": 3297, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ben_Healy\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.132496485512619e-26, \"text\": \"Ben Healy\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q13415036\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ben_Healy\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ben_Healy\"}, {\"begin\": 3299, \"end\": 3306, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ireland_national_rugby_union_team\", \"score\": 0.5487663862383653, \"rank\": 0.7198156884449738, \"text\": \"Ireland\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ireland_national_rugby_union_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ireland_national_rugby_union_team\"}, {\"begin\": 3447, \"end\": 3456, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ben_Healy\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.132496485512619e-26, \"text\": \"Ben Healy\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q13415036\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ben_Healy\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ben_Healy\"}, {\"begin\": 3476, \"end\": 3486, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kazakhstan\", \"score\": 0.9999673805914127, \"rank\": 3.262029133117916e-05, \"text\": \"Kazakhstan\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kazakhstan\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kazakhstan\"}, {\"begin\": 3489, \"end\": 3504, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alexey_Lutsenko\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Alexey Lutsenko\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alexey_Lutsenko\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alexey_Lutsenko\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Their move set off numerous counters in the bunch and, with small four-rider teams and no race radio, there was an edge of chaos to the peloton.\", \"from\": 3506, \"to\": 3650, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Evenepoel's first surge came with 67km to go and it shattered the peloton behind him, forcing many to ride fast through a feed zone and miss valuable resources.\", \"from\": 3652, \"to\": 3812, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"But he soon let up and Healy and Lutsenko were allowed to stay 40 seconds clear.\", \"from\": 3813, \"to\": 3893, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Then came a key move.\", \"from\": 3895, \"to\": 3916, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Madous and a few others - Fred Wright (Great Britain), Michael Woods (Canada), Nils Politt (Germany), Stefan Kung (Switzerland) and Marco Haller (Austria) - raced away from the main bunch and caught up with Healy and Lutsenko while Evenepoel and Belgian teammate Wout van Aert missed the moment, as did Dutchman Van der Poel.\", \"from\": 3917, \"to\": 4242, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3943, \"end\": 3954, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Fred_Wright_(cyclist)\", \"score\": 0.9999956969842781, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Fred Wright\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Fred_Wright_(cyclist)\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Fred_Wright_(cyclist)\"}, {\"begin\": 3956, \"end\": 3969, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Great_Britain\", \"score\": 0.9996889662220507, \"rank\": 0.00031043769453351164, \"text\": \"Great Britain\", \"types\": [\"Q23442\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Great_Britain\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Great_Britain\"}, {\"begin\": 3972, \"end\": 3985, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Michael_Woods_(DJ)\", \"score\": 0.6748750082199441, \"rank\": 0.33912275537233105, \"text\": \"Michael Woods\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q483501\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Michael_Woods_(DJ)\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Michael_Woods_(DJ)\"}, {\"begin\": 3987, \"end\": 3993, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Canada\", \"score\": 0.9838661557330458, \"rank\": 0.016379987320109136, \"text\": \"Canada\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Canada\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Canada\"}, {\"begin\": 4019, \"end\": 4025, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Stefan_Salvatore\", \"score\": 0.9999997972190818, \"rank\": 2.0278078857261573e-07, \"text\": \"Stefan\", \"types\": [\"Q95074\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Stefan_Salvatore\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Stefan_Salvatore\"}, {\"begin\": 4032, \"end\": 4043, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/A1_Team_Switzerland\", \"score\": 0.5601846621288978, \"rank\": 0.7816110963784924, \"text\": \"Switzerland\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/A1_Team_Switzerland\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/A1_Team_Switzerland\"}, {\"begin\": 4049, \"end\": 4061, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Marco_Haller_(cyclist)\", \"score\": 0.9999960452233594, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Marco Haller\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Marco_Haller_(cyclist)\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Marco_Haller_(cyclist)\"}, {\"begin\": 4063, \"end\": 4070, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Austria\", \"score\": 0.9945527367608282, \"rank\": 0.0054759490973120715, \"text\": \"Austria\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Austria\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Austria\"}, {\"begin\": 4163, \"end\": 4170, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Belgium\", \"score\": 0.9972631080383573, \"rank\": 0.0027443718547404163, \"text\": \"Belgian\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Belgium\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Belgium\"}, {\"begin\": 4180, \"end\": 4193, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Wout_van_Aert\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Wout van Aert\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Wout_van_Aert\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Wout_van_Aert\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Evenepoel decided enough was enough.\", \"from\": 4244, \"to\": 4280, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The rest tried to follow his attack but soon he had bridged over to the leaders and he hit the front on a sharp climb.\", \"from\": 4281, \"to\": 4399, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Behind him, a string of high-quality riders stood, pumping their pedals, tongues lolling while Evenepoel sat in his seat seemingly oblivious to the pain, with all the serenity of a man who did not know his hat was on fire.\", \"from\": 4400, \"to\": 4622, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Madouas clung on valiantly to his wheel, understandably refusing to share the workload with a frustrated Evenepoel as they led the race.\", \"from\": 4624, \"to\": 4760, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4624, \"end\": 4631, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Valentin_Madouas\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Madouas\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Valentin_Madouas\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Valentin_Madouas\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The Frenchman would not, and he probably could not, eventually falling away too.\", \"from\": 4761, \"to\": 4841, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Back down the road, Van der Poel tried to surge but even his hardest effort did not reduce Evenepoel's by-now huge advantage.\", \"from\": 4842, \"to\": 4967, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Even a puncture could not stop him.\", \"from\": 4968, \"to\": 5003, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The rider who had never raced in France before this year capped an extraordinary month with a second gold medal.\", \"from\": 5005, \"to\": 5117, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 5038, \"end\": 5044, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France_national_rugby_union_team\", \"score\": 0.9767478196709908, \"rank\": 0.015283013564636294, \"text\": \"France\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France_national_rugby_union_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France_national_rugby_union_team\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He is the first man to win both races in the same Olympics.\", \"from\": 5118, \"to\": 5177, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The World Championships are next, and his season could yet get sweeter.\", \"from\": 5178, \"to\": 5249, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Join thought-provoking conversations, follow other Independent readers and see their replies  Please refresh the page or navigate to another page on the site to be automatically logged inPlease refresh your browser to be logged in\", \"from\": 5251, \"to\": 5481, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 5302, \"end\": 5313, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/The_Independent\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.8320669852552297e-15, \"text\": \"Independent\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\", \"Q234460\", \"Q11032\", \"Q1092563\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/The_Independent\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/The_Independent\"}]}]}"